{
  "title": "Spicy Dense Show-off Algerian Garlic Stir-fry",
  "description": "A show-stopping vegan and gluten-free dish featuring a blend of spices, creamy soured cream, and tangy chive dip that comes together in a vibrant garlic stir-fry.",
  "cuisine": "Algerian",
  "diet": [
    "jain-friendly"
